Royal Mail Plans to Cut Up to 3,500 Jobs in Revamp, Sky Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-03-21T18:27:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/royal-mail-plans-to-cut-up-to-3-500-jobs-in-revamp-sky-reports.html
Royal Mail Group Ltd. is to cut up
to 3,500 jobs as part of a reorganization program to address its
deteriorating financial position, Sky News City Editor Mark
Kleinman  reported  on his blog on the website, without
attribution.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
